sub_title: Customer Service Representative at Dow Benelux || Microsoft Community Translator || Italian-English-Spanish
summary: In addition to my great passion for travel, photography and the environment, I have widened my horizons by venturing into the world of foreign languages, especially English and Spanish. During my university career, I have acquired language and cultural skills mainly in the fields of medicine, tourism, the environment and information technology. My aim and desire is to work in administration, international relations, as well as translation, in the hope of being able to give my contribution to an ever-growing multicultural society.
